column4: Upstart Holdings, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, operates a cloud-based artificial intelligence (AI) lending platform in the United States. The company operates through three segments: Personal Lending, Auto Lending, and Other. Its platform includes personal loans, automotive retail and refinance loans, home equity lines of credit, and small dollar loans. Upstart Holdings, Inc. was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in San Mateo, California.
